Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:39.42,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(252,241.5)\fad(450,500)}全力暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是领主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是精灵啊 精灵 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:04.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们也跟来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的公主殿下 独占真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也分给我们一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:20.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者们下一个目标应该是 加多尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是把矮人族给解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但那里是奥尔特最大的兵工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,防御很坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:38.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者可是捉摸不透的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:44.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那里沦陷了的话 这个国家就彻底完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这批兵器也是要送上西方战场的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:12.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我国的海上运输舰队好像全军覆没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有多少武器和防具都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且上头命令要增大基本产量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要让矮人族们制造更多的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再继续压榨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会一个接一个地死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经有好几个人都死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矿山塌陷么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:55.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所土间的泥土 欧派米的硫磺 木炭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,三样东西一旦具备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,便能造黑色火药了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火药最大的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:20.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,并非烧身的火焰 也不是飞溅的破片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:25.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,突击 给我扯大嗓门喊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人陷入恐慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加把劲冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:43.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,声音和火光 冲击和畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那和石火矢 棒火矢 还有火枪的道理是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.03,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(446.4,5.4)}注：石火矢 棒火矢 种子岛火枪，均是武器名称。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是岛津 种子岛火枪的盛行之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很清楚这个道理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,冲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人 敌袭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是精灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是造反的那群家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这么可怕的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在精心制作着这么可怕的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,小心地做喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然大家会一起上西天的 小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:33.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 没问题 精灵的手很巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 尽情地射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是把火药附在箭上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把棒火矢的用法借鉴过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:48.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上与一和精灵的技术便可发挥出令人畏惧的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:52.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 连这里都能听到烧东西吵杂声还真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的物资明明可以为我们所用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是浪费 啊 真是浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫吧 叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加剧恐慌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要爆炸了啊 火势越来越大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊 到处都是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀光的 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:21.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要等他们恢复士气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躏他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 情况很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是城池 进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去拿下城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:59.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是奥尔特的大型兵工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:03.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们奥尔特党 武装亲卫兵团镇守的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会被你们这种反贼攻下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:19.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,重甲 大刀 长枪 无弓 无矢 无马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:23.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:31.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和废城的那帮家伙一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:39.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就可以发挥奥尔米擅长的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石棺之奥尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,单论石壁符术能力的话 她可是当世第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:56.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上 她是你们之中最有才能的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 一股老流氓的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:04.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是实际为83岁的老头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,扔进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人崩溃了 这是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好机会可值千金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,重装兵全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…什么啊 那个到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,门…把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把石壁那样用么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用防御术来把敌人赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:43.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像是一个为打倒敌人而生的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是城门关上的话还真是难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子 覆盆子好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他要跟过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,痴呆的南蛮人有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,传令 传令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向奥尔米传令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盆子 我要更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有了 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有覆盆子的话 迦太基可是要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对着这里说话就可以了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个球是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米说对着讲话就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 欧派 喂 听到了么 派欧米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,记住我的名字啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石壁符还有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,按着我的指示做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一的弓术和你的符结合起来就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,城门正在关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个爆炸到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经放了狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然距离援军到达还有半日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们关上了城门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该就过不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把那些家伙困于城外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:26.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,墙壁外驻扎地的士兵已经溃败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,城内之兵也只有少量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看我联合援军把他们包饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,墙壁上有阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信先生 好厉害啊 信先生 信先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 虽然石壁也非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这边才真的强吧 无论怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要传令兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:56.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 最好不过的就是传令是即时的 没有时间差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有注意到么 术师们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是非常了不起的玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕这是思考角度的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙应该想也没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:11.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只把这当做可以使研究和报告尽早传达的便利的球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,使得分离的军队协调起来成为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情他们从来都没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮 实在干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石壁也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米把那个作为防御壁来使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而丰久把其当做投射器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后现在则是作为攻城的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:37.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作为外来技术的携带者的同时 也是思维的差异者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那些家伙口中的废弃物又到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为什么要身处于这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又要我们做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这才是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是你们出现在那里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,个体差异使万物蜕变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去扰乱一切吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抹消掉这个世界的「应有的样子」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让这个世界转动吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1224,995.1)}Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城池 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰先生 我们去解放矮人族那帮人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是些强壮的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们精灵族从小就听说很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的确很讨厌矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:44.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都怀着恐惧与侮辱地听父母诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:48.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那也包含着精灵族对自己没有之物的羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的强壮身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的顽强意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们锐利的斧头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该就被囚禁在这个工坊都市内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:02.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,过去我们不敢想象精灵族和矮人族会有并肩作战的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们本来的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去解放他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:13.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族既鄙俗又暴力 胡子乱糟糟地既肮脏又野蛮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大口喝酒大口吃饭 又臭又可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用其粗壮的手臂碎石打铁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用其粗壮的双腿踏在这片大地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挥动大斧把敌人劈成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:32.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再回去边豪饮边笑着放声高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是哪栋建筑都是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是名为工坊的监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族在我们精灵族投降了之后还在继续反抗着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了农奴的我们的处境比他们要好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:57.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都一直在矿山或者工坊里进行酷役吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:00.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想外面的骚动是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:08.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真讽刺 事到如今你们来解救我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:13.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「我们」 我们也是被拯救的一方 被漂流者们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论谁都可以 解放我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:23.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受够了 解放我们吧 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}只有劳动才是通向自由的路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:29.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了 即使你们是精灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:33.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,解放我们 老夫我们也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是矮人族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的胡子真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:43.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,长得也不高 消瘦得很严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你就是那个「漂流者」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们擅自这样称呼我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗前就应该吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭吧 吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 欧派米 怎么了 城市攻陷下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 欧派米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:16.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 丰久他貌似解放了矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:22.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族貌似都饿得不行 丰久就大喊吃饭吃饭这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:27.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非 莫非现在都在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还没有攻陷下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,食料仓库和我们带过来的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有煮剩下的食物都翻了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都扔到锅里开始煮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就在敌人的面前吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 马 马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自把运货的马还有军马都宰来煮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙果然是个笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷 我把覆盆子都拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作为奖励就把高卢赏赐给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(532.8,0.6)}高卢：拉丁语Gallia，古代西欧地区名，法国、比利时等地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做成粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加多点热水做成粥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会因为太饿导致消化不良而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:17.46,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,193.5)}在下猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:17.46,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(146.4,152.7)}大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以前猴子他说他就遭受过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,由于太饿了大口吃饭差点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族死了就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:26.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵 听好了 让他们好好咀嚼再吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,森兰丸 我也想吃泡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我不在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道啊蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:41.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好想吃米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,米饭是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,泡饭又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:55.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些烟是什么 他们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经解放了矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们都在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在还不逃跑的话等我们吃完饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就会把你们全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走的人我是不会追杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把武器都丢掉空手逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快点做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在矮人族他们的眼中只有饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,离吃完饭已经没有多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完饭下一个目标就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一副连你们的内脏都要吃掉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 这家伙才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全知全能都为了战斗而特化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打开城门还是去死 快决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第一大门已经被突破的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经没有时间等待援军的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,兵长 等矮人族吃饱后就会攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被他们挖了地道 迟早也会攻陷这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被全部杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者 你会放过我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打开城门的话就会让我们逃走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战场的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不会砍手无寸铁的降兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:38.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后地方官又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:43.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我把城门打开了 能放我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那你们开个小酒席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要给你准备切腹的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们都会等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,切 切腹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,介错的话我会瞬间帮你解决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.41,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(508.8,15)}介錯： 为切腹自杀者断头（的人），为了减少他的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要切腹 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:01.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为城池沦陷了啊 城池守将切腹谢罪不是常识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,守将承担责任这是义务 是荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 一定要切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会乖乖切下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,行 你没有切腹的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有作为守将的气度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有留下首级的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要去追击他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过会放他们逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出尔反尔就前功尽废了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为以前的坏毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以前总是让我干这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有人让你干那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「我们」的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一 追击怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:31.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,带着符咒的空中侦查骑兵在到处飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:34.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒还有法术都不要用 会被侦查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这工作真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也因为你们是十月机关 所以才接下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的冒险者公会的任务实在是太烦了 不想接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 多古
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是方便的望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:53.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是十月机关里传说中的「遗物」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜龙 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是末席 但也是六大龙之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,它也加入黑王军旗下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为青铜龙的加入所以停止向南进攻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你看一看「北壁」的南边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:21.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么 是我眼睛出问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是农田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物居然在耕地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怪物的文明化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物们开始进行原始的耕种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王那帮家伙在那里 在北壁那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正如大师傅大人所说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他和以往的废弃物都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他并不是一心想要毁灭世界的废弃物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想要取代人类成为怪物的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
